The paper also mentions the use of weights and voting, which are common techniques in statistical learning and optimization, leading to the third likely category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper deals with meeting recordings, which are a type of multimedia data, leading to the fourth likely category of cs.MM (Multimedia).
